Introduction

Chaei is a South Korean singer and rapper under CMG Stars. She is a member of the girl group LOVE ONE.

She is a former member of the girl group eite under EVA Entertainment, which she left on August 18, 2024 along with all the other members. During her time with the group, she had the stage name Chaehyun, which is also her birth name.
